**APIStabilityScope**  
**Description:**  
Monitors API endpoints for stability over time and flags unusual behavior, error streaks, or jitter trends.

```markdown
# APIStabilityScope - Long-Term API Reliability Monitor

APIStabilityScope evaluates long-running endpoints and visualizes shifts in reliability or performance.

## Features
- Error pattern tracking  
- Response time distribution  
- Export to CSV or JSON

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/APIStabilityScope.git
cd APIStabilityScope
python monitor.py
